Package: mwbenchr
Title: Metabolomics Workbench REST API Interface
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Dany", "Mukesha", , "danymukesha@gmail.com", 
            role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0001-9514-751X"))
Description: Provides a user-friendly interface to the Metabolomics Workbench
    REST API, enabling programmatic access to metabolomics data from R. 
    The package covers all API endpoints including compound information, 
    study metadata, RefMet standardization, and mass spectrometry searches.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
